# ğŸ“· CameraX Custom Camera App (Kotlin)

This Android app demonstrates a **custom camera screen** built with **CameraX** and **Kotlin**, supporting:

- Fullscreen camera preview
- Manual photo capture (shutter button)
- Zoom slider (1x to 5x)
- Manual focus slider (fallback to auto-focus)
- Tap-to-focus functionality
- 3x3 rule-of-thirds grid overlay (drawn programmatically)
- Supports Android 10 to 16 (API 29 to 35)

